'''Silicartha''' was a special type of [[Silica/Legends|silica]]-based poison developed on the planet [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. [[Moisture farmer/Legends|Moisture farmers]] used it to kill small creatures like [[sand-borer]]s that would burrow into their [[hydroponics garden]]s. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] once tricked an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer into believing that he had taken some in order to blackmail him into accessing the [[Krake Data Vault|data vault]] on [[Krake's Planet]].

